{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My name is Joseph,\na Member of Parliament in Kenya."},{"time":3000,"text":"Picture a Maasai village,"},{"time":4999,"text":"and one evening,"},{"time":6579,"text":"government soldiers come,\nsurround the village"},{"time":9000,"text":"and ask each elder to bring\none boy to school."},{"time":11215,"text":"That's how I went to school --"},{"time":13000,"text":"pretty much a government guy\npointing a gun"},{"time":15024,"text":"and told my father,\n\"You have to make a choice.\""},{"time":17287,"text":"I walked very comfortably\nto this missionary school,"},{"time":20000,"text":"that was run by an American missionary."},{"time":22000,"text":"The first thing the American missionary\ngave me was a candy."},{"time":25000,"text":"I had never in my life ever tasted candy."},{"time":27000,"text":"So I said to myself,\nwith all these hundred other boys,"},{"time":29644,"text":"this is where I belong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31030,"text":"(Laughter) I stayed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32856,"text":"When everybody else was dropping out."},{"time":35000,"text":"My family moved; we're nomads."},{"time":36745,"text":"It was a boarding school, I was seven --"},{"time":38722,"text":"Every time it closed\nyou had to travel to find them."},{"time":41435,"text":"40-50 miles, it doesn't matter."},{"time":43000,"text":"You slept in the bush, but you kept going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45519,"text":"And I stayed. I don't know why, but I did."},{"time":48000,"text":"All of a sudden I passed\nthe national examination,"},{"time":52000,"text":"found myself in a very beautiful\nhigh school in Kenya."},{"time":55000,"text":"And I finished high school."},{"time":56908,"text":"And just walking, I found a man"},{"time":58750,"text":"who gave me a full scholarship\nto the United States."},{"time":61617,"text":"My mother still lived in a cow-dung hut,"},{"time":63659,"text":"none of my brothers were going to school,"},{"time":65706,"text":"and this man told me, \"Here, go.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"I got a scholarship"},{"time":69059,"text":"to St. Lawrence University,\nUpstate New York;"},{"time":71723,"text":"finished that."},{"time":73325,"text":"And after that I went\nto Harvard Graduate School;"},{"time":77000,"text":"finished that."},{"time":78674,"text":"Then I worked in DC a little bit:"},{"time":80421,"text":"I wrote a book for National Geographic\nand taught U.S. history."},{"time":83507,"text":"And every time, I kept going back home,"},{"time":86157,"text":"listening to their problems --"},{"time":87650,"text":"sick people, people\nwith no water, all this stuff --"},{"time":90220,"text":"every time I go back to America,"},{"time":92164,"text":"I kept thinking about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93640,"text":"Then one day, an elder gave me\na story that went like this:"},{"time":97365,"text":"long time ago, there was a big war\nbetween tribes."},{"time":101524,"text":"This specific tribe was really afraid\nof this other Luhya tribe."},{"time":105000,"text":"Every time, they sent scouts\nto make sure no one attacked them."},{"time":108564,"text":"So one day, the scouts came running\nand told the villagers,"},{"time":111552,"text":"\"The enemies are coming.\nOnly half an hour away, they'll be here.\""},{"time":114753,"text":"So people scrambled, took their things\nand ready to go, move out."},{"time":118579,"text":"But there were two men:"},{"time":120330,"text":"one man was blind, one man had no legs"},{"time":122822,"text":"-- he was born like that."},{"time":124151,"text":"The leader of the chiefs said, \"No, sorry.\nWe can't take you. You'll slow us down."},{"time":128072,"text":"We have to flee our women\nand children, we have to run.\""},{"time":132318,"text":"And they were left behind, waiting to die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"But these two people worked something out."},{"time":138000,"text":"The blind man said, \"Look,\nI'm a very strong man but I can't see.\""},{"time":141167,"text":"The man with no legs says,\n\"I can see as far as the end of the world,"},{"time":144477,"text":"but I can't save myself\nfrom a cat, or whatever animals.\""},{"time":149595,"text":"The blind man went down\non his knees like this,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and told the man with no legs\nto go over his back, and stood up."},{"time":156380,"text":"The man on top can see,\nthe blind man can walk."},{"time":159791,"text":"These guys took off, followed\nthe footsteps of the villagers"},{"time":162672,"text":"until they found and passed them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"So, this was told to me\nin a setup of elders."},{"time":171000,"text":"And it's a really poor area."},{"time":172719,"text":"I represent Northern Kenya:"},{"time":174199,"text":"the most nomadic, remote areas\nyou can even find."},{"time":178000,"text":"And that man told me, \"So, here you are."},{"time":180000,"text":"You've got a good education from America,\nyou have a good life in America;"},{"time":183968,"text":"what are you going to do for us?"},{"time":187087,"text":"We want you to be our eyes,\nwe'll give you the legs."},{"time":190000,"text":"We'll walk you, you lead us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":192412,"text":"The opportunity came.\nI was always thinking about that:"},{"time":195046,"text":"\"What can I do to help my people?"},{"time":197000,"text":"Every time you go to an area\nwhere for 43 years of independence,"},{"time":200371,"text":"we still don't have\nbasic health facilities."},{"time":202937,"text":"A man has to be transported\nin a wheelbarrow 30 km for a hospital."},{"time":206088,"text":"No clean drinking water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207700,"text":"So I said, \"I'm going to dedicate myself."},{"time":210000,"text":"I'm leaving America."},{"time":211571,"text":"I'm going to run for office.\""},{"time":213404,"text":"Last June, I moved from America,"},{"time":217229,"text":"ran in July election and won."},{"time":220603,"text":"And I came for them,"},{"time":224127,"text":"and that's my goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225278,"text":"Right now I have in place,\nfor the last nine months,"},{"time":228825,"text":"a plan that in five years,"},{"time":232040,"text":"every nomad will have\nclean drinking water."},{"time":235444,"text":"We're building dispensaries\nacross that constituency."},{"time":239490,"text":"I'm asking my friends from America to help"},{"time":241744,"text":"with bringing nurses\nor doctors to help us out."},{"time":244291,"text":"I'm trying to improve infrastructure."},{"time":246936,"text":"I'm using the knowledge\nI received from the United States"},{"time":249676,"text":"and from my community"},{"time":251328,"text":"to move them forward."},{"time":252753,"text":"I'm trying to develop\nhomegrown solutions to our issues"},{"time":256235,"text":"because people from outside\ncan come and help us,"},{"time":258825,"text":"but if we don't help ourselves,\nthere's nothing to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261928,"text":"My plan right now"},{"time":263040,"text":"as I continue with introducing\nstudents to different fields --"},{"time":267000,"text":"some become doctors, some lawyers --"},{"time":268874,"text":"we want to produce\na comprehensive group of people,"},{"time":271294,"text":"students who can come back\nand help us see a community grow"},{"time":274174,"text":"that is in the middle\nof a huge economic recession."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277817,"text":"As I continue to be\na Member of Parliament"},{"time":280634,"text":"and as I continue listening\nto all of you talking about botany,"},{"time":284024,"text":"health, democracy, new inventions,"},{"time":287479,"text":"I'm hoping that one day\nin my own little community --"},{"time":290000,"text":"which is 26,000 square km,"},{"time":292000,"text":"maybe five times Rhode Island --"},{"time":294161,"text":"with no roads,"},{"time":295650,"text":"we'll be able to become a model\nto help others develop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299603,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300988,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}